metadata.name: First Step
metadata.description:
Before the photo shoot, Victoria said she was shy for the camera. When she took off her light dress I was very surprised.

It turned out that this shy girl had nothing under her dress, she was completely naked. 
I immediately understood why shy girls are considered the sexiest. Of course I was silent, but my inner voice was truly jubilant.

She took the picture frame, whispered "I want to do this together, my first step" and turned her back to me. 
I took the camera and took that picture.

"First Step"


6545  x  4363 , 1/1 NFTs
